Parameter Value Type

Parameters offer a versatile way to reuse components and manage how updates are implemented according to your requirements.

Value type, in parameter settings, defines acceptable parameter values and how theyâ€™re used to update the component.

VALUE TYPE	DESCRIPTION
Dynamic	Set up parameters to enable components to interact with dashboard queries.
